window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Out in the Wild Lands, Boyd's life has taken a riveting turn. No longer content to be the mere caretaker for his S-Ranked girlfriend, he seizes the chance to rekindle the flames of his Heroic ambitions. The call to glory beckons, and Boyd finds himself on a journey that promises not only fame but a legacy that will echo through the ages.</p> <p>Charged with the electrifying task of leading a team comprised of both allies and lovers, Boyd steps into a world rife with challenges and opportunities. The stage is set for his rise to Heroic greatness as he races against time to rescue an old friend, avenge a grieving widow, and face off against a fearsome dragon of mythic proportions. With every foe he overcomes, he inches closer to the status he craves.</p> <p>Backed by his loyal Devoted, Boyd confronts the legendary Last Dragon, an adversary who tests his mettle in ways he never could have imagined. As The Devoted’s exploits garner attention, their reputation spreads like wildfire, but Boyd soon realizes that fame comes at a price. Dark forces conspire, and a vengeful figure with a toxic sense of entitlement seeks to derail Boyd's path to glory—setting the stage for a cataclysmic showdown.</p> <p>In this adrenaline-fueled saga, Boyd grapples not only with external foes but also with his own doubts and desires. The bonds of his team are stretched to their limits, and allegiances will be tested. With every decision he makes, the intricate web of fate tightens around him, leading to a breathtaking crescendo where the ultimate test of Heroism awaits. Will Boyd be strong enough to withstand it?</p>"; 
